Yorick was a doctor that became an skeleton when trying to resurrect someone. Now he carries some of his/her bones as a bow/boomerang.

Skill 1: resucitate some minions as skeletons.
Skill 2: arrow that goes straight hitting everything on the way.
Skill 3: to-be-determined-aura affecting his own revives.
Skill 4: boomerang. Short rage, returns when hitting one.
